GRO will acknowledge the email complaint with 48 hours and will resolve the complaint
          within 30 days of raising the complaint.
GRO will internally check the resolution provided by Customer Care Executive in the
          previous complaint and reason for raising a complaint by Customer again.
GRO will thoroughly investigate in detail the issue raised and make all efforts to provide an
          amicable solution to the Customer through an email.
Customer also has an option of calling the GRO on the number provided above in office
          working hours.
